references: Related: CF 168908. Amending: Ord 42337. Repealing: Ord 66735, Ord 67006
summary: An ordinance relating to the harbor and waterfront of the City of Seattle; designating certain locations as "oil docks"; correcting the designation of Union Oil Company Dock; amending Section 38 of Ordinance No. 42337, as amended, and repealing Ordinances Nos. 66735 and 67006.
